column2: select top # albums.album as album, sum(albums.TrackPrice) as AlbumPrice, count(albums.album) as num,albums.ArtistName as Artist  from (select a.Title as album, t.UnitPrice as TrackPrice, ar.Name as ArtistName  from chinook.Track as t  inner join chinook.Album as a on a.AlbumId = t.AlbumId  inner join chinook.Artist as ar on ar.ArtistId = a.ArtistId)   albums group by albums.album, ArtistName  order by AlbumPrice DESC
